Changelog

0.5.0 "Horizon" (2020-01-18)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* New: It is now possible to review package dependencies (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=61)
* New: It is now possible to search for files in packages' contents (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=176)
* New: Tests for checking syntax of Perl sources and templates (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=183)
* New: Social network sharing links for news and packages (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=177)
* Change: Site is now completely rewritten in HTML5 (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=148)
* Change: Register packages by default with regpkg utility
* Fix: Fix download URLs in English locale (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=181)
* Fix: Fix Base64 encoding of mirror logo on download page (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=182)
* Fix: Update view definitions for MySQL 8.0.13 (no ASC or DESC in ORDER BY)
* Fix: Remove display width for INT (deprecated as of MySQL 8.0.17)

0.4.6 (2018-05-19)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* New: Packages including security fixes are now marked and highlighted in 
       latest packages, searches, package details and feeds (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=179)
* Change: Make feed titles distinguishable between architectures

0.4.5 (2018-02-18)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* New: Add social networks sharing links for the site (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=177)
* Change: Initial support for HTML5 (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=148)

0.4.4 (2017-01-09)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* New: Software series support
* New: Obfuscate package and news author emails (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=73)
* New: Add information for repositories access with Slackpkg
* New: Possibility to search for exact terms in double quotes (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=169)
* Change: Show only latest package builds by default in searches
* Change: Split latest packages for 32 and 64 bit architectures (see
          bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=168)
* Fix: Option 'Only latest' in Advanced search was not working (see
       bug https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=167)

0.4.3 "Dobromira" (2014-01-17)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix: slapt-get cannot download packages from SlackPack repositories due to
       wrong file location in PACKAGES.TXT (see
       bug 141 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=141)
* Fix: A JavaScript error on window.open in IE for Verify MD5 functionality

0.4.2 (2011-10-11)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Change: Modifications is URLs related to 64-bit support
* Change: Show only active mirrors

0.4.1 (2010-09-06)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Change: No URL to licenses without online definition - only description
* Change: Add links to define "GPL only" option for advanced searching
* Change: Display available information during package registration and
          provide the option to reuse it or not
* New: Add script for synchronization of LinuxPackages FTP

0.4.0 "Mihaela" (2010-08-21)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* New: Support for different package compressions - tbz, tgz, tlz and txz
       (see bugs  91 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=91,
                  92 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=92,
                  93 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=93,
                 112 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=112)
* New: Bulgarian localization - at least
       (see bug 58 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=58)
* New: Console package registration utility
       (see bug 55 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=55)
* New: Categorization by vendor
       (bug 83 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=83)
* New: Possibility for donation through PayPal
       (bug 90 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=90)
* New: LinuxPackages synchronization script
* New: SlackPack Data Model for MySQL Workbench
* Fix: Gracefully fail in case the database is not running
       (bug 78 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=78)
* Fix: Searching without terms causes internal server error
       (bug 79 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=79)
* Fix: Proper generation of PACKAGES.TXT with totals
       (see bug 112 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=112)
* Fix: Various fixes and small improvements
       (bugs  80 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=80,
              89 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=89,
             107 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=107,
             108 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=108)

0.3.2 (2007-10-08)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* New: Some more links in the Links section
* Change: Package counts now show only 'active' packages. Active package is
          one that is currently not obsoleted or deleted.
          (Bug 77 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=77)
* Fix: FILELIST.TXT and CHECKSUMS.md5 files are now aligned in columns

0.3.1 (2007-07-03)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * Fix: Unpublished news can get into feeds (Bug 74 - http://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=74)
 * Fix: Some interface layout fixes

0.3.0 (2007-04-19)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * New: Package statuses (Bug 60 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=60 )
 * New: MD5 verification (Bug 38 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=38 )
 * New: Package signature review (Bug 57 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=57 )
 * New: Donating options (Bug 62 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=62 )
 * New: Advanced search will now have new functionality, which will be used
        by default - latest only will list only latest packages by name,
        architecture and format (Bug 56 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=56 )
 * Fix: News page functionality (Bug 54 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=54 )
 * Fix: Multiprotocol mirrors (Bug 59 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=59 )
 * Fix: Mirrors info (Bug 51 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=51 )
 * Fix: Unicode problem (Bug 65 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=65 )

0.2.2 (2007-02-08)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * Fix: Fix news links in the feeds (Bug 53 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=53 )
 * Fix: Re-fix history and other formats separation (Bug 45 - https://sotirov-bg.net/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=45 )

0.2.1 (2007-02-05)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * Fix: Fix for broken site functionality after the mirrors support

0.2.0 (2007-02-04)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * New: Mirrors support - now the user can choose from where to download
 * New: Header navigation menu with buttons

